  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat and add cumin seeds, coriander seeds, cinnamon stick, and cardamom pods. Roast for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger to the pan and sauté until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add Hyderabadi white yam to the pan and sauté for 5 minutes until it starts to brown.",
    "Add turmeric powder, red chili powder, and garam masala powder to the pan and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the pan and bring to a boil.",
    "Add basmati rice to the pan and cook for 10 minutes until the water is absorbed.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a smoking chamber or a charcoal grill and smoke for 30 minutes.",
    "Fluff the biryani with a fork and serve hot."
  ],
